articles.summary: Anybody who has been looking at mortgages recently may have noticed something surprising. articles.summary: Back Vietnam International Bank (VIB) would like to inform you of the change to SMS notification service in your current account balance (SMS Banking) for individual customers and micro-, small and medium-sized enterprises (MSMEs) according to the regulations of VIB from time to time as follows: - SMS alerts will be stopped in terms of informing changes in account balances caused by money transfers between your own current accounts and term deposit accounts. SMS alerts for balance changes resulting from other transactions remain unaffected.
